### Basis Gesundheitscheck
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### Gesundheitscheck mit curl
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health \
    -H "Accept: application/json"

### Detaillierter Gesundheitscheck
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: health-check-001

### Gesundheitscheck mit zusätzlichen Headers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: health-check-002
User-Agent: HealthMonitor/1.0
X-Environment: testing

### Gesundheitscheck für Monitoring
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache
X-Monitor-ID: monitor-001
